1
00:01:41,680 --> 00:01:43,280
Pharmacy Master Li

2
00:01:43,280 --> 00:01:46,560
Our Medicine Master Ye is resting and recovering

3
00:01:46,560 --> 00:01:48,519
Whatever it is, you can speak with me.

4
00:01:48,519 --> 00:01:50,359
The internal affairs of the Mystic Medicine Association

5
00:01:50,359 --> 00:01:52,719
are not for you to dictate.

6
00:01:57,200 --> 00:01:57,840
What's going on?

7
00:02:01,400 --> 00:02:02,560
Medicine Master Ye.

8
00:02:02,560 --> 00:02:04,000
We sincerely apologize

9
00:02:04,000 --> 00:02:05,640
for disturbing your recovery.

10
00:02:05,640 --> 00:02:06,760
The matter is urgent,

11
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:08,319
and we had no other choice.

12
00:02:12,840 --> 00:02:15,159
What crime have I, Ye Zhentian,

13
00:02:15,159 --> 00:02:17,199
committed that's so grave

14
00:02:18,000 --> 00:02:21,879
to warrant so many Medicine Masters of the Association

15
00:02:21,879 --> 00:02:23,599
storming over to interrogate me?

16
00:02:31,719 --> 00:02:32,800
At the Medicine King Ceremony,

17
00:02:32,800 --> 00:02:34,840
hundreds of people were poisoned

18
00:02:34,840 --> 00:02:35,840
and put in grave danger.

19
00:02:37,159 --> 00:02:38,240
The medicines for the ceremony

20
00:02:38,240 --> 00:02:39,919
have always been managed by your Green Wood Hall.

21
00:02:40,960 --> 00:02:42,120
Medicine Master Ye,

22
00:02:42,120 --> 00:02:44,000
wouldn't you say that's a serious charge?

23
00:02:46,319 --> 00:02:48,120
And how do we know

24
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:49,759
this wasn't a setup of your own design

25
00:02:49,759 --> 00:02:51,159
to frame us?

26
00:02:53,120 --> 00:02:54,439
Miss Ye,

27
00:02:54,439 --> 00:02:56,360
watch your words.

28
00:02:56,360 --> 00:02:57,719
How could the Red Fire Hall's hand

29
00:02:57,719 --> 00:02:59,479
ever reach into your Green Wood Hall?

30
00:02:59,919 --> 00:03:00,759
Besides,

31
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:04,000
the ones who pointed out the tainted herbs at the ceremony

32
00:03:04,000 --> 00:03:05,120
were you and him.

33
00:03:21,199 --> 00:03:22,159
This pack of medicinal herbs,

34
00:03:22,159 --> 00:03:24,840
I personally took from Green Wood Hall's storeroom.

35
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:28,800
Everyone is welcome to inspect it.

36
00:04:06,039 --> 00:04:07,319
All of you, take a good look.

37
00:04:10,159 --> 00:04:12,960
Every herb pouch from our Green Wood Hall

38
00:04:12,960 --> 00:04:14,639
bears the special Hall Seal of Green Wood Hall.

39
00:04:16,399 --> 00:04:18,839
And before any herb is stored away,

40
00:04:18,839 --> 00:04:20,000
it's photographed and archived.

41
00:04:21,759 --> 00:04:24,000
I wonder, did the herb Medicine Master Lu just used

42
00:04:24,839 --> 00:04:25,600
bear our Hall Seal?

43
00:04:44,399 --> 00:04:45,199
No.

44
00:05:08,439 --> 00:05:10,040
The old fox really knows his tricks.

45
00:05:10,839 --> 00:05:12,240
I was actually thinking

46
00:05:12,240 --> 00:05:14,040
if Medicine Master Ye confessed,

47
00:05:14,040 --> 00:05:15,160
I'd let you save face.

48
00:05:15,160 --> 00:05:17,839
But it seems that won't work now.

49
00:05:17,839 --> 00:05:18,720
Medicine Master Lu,

50
00:05:22,040 --> 00:05:23,560
bring up that wretched son of mine.

51
00:05:31,120 --> 00:05:31,920
Uncle Ye.

52
00:05:32,680 --> 00:05:33,360
Lu Mingcheng.

53
00:05:33,360 --> 00:05:34,120
Uncle Ye.

54
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,120
Uncle Ye, you have to save me!

55
00:05:35,120 --> 00:05:36,040
Uncle Ye.

56
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:37,920
I swapped the Medicine King Ceremony herbs for you!

57
00:05:37,920 --> 00:05:38,480
Uncle Ye.

58
00:05:38,480 --> 00:05:39,199
Please save me!

59
00:05:41,000 --> 00:05:42,959
You worthless piece of trash.

60
00:05:42,959 --> 00:05:44,680
A treacherous, ungrateful son.

61
00:05:44,680 --> 00:05:47,160
Is this how you repay me for raising you?

62
00:05:47,160 --> 00:05:48,639
Conspiring with outsiders

63
00:05:49,360 --> 00:05:50,759
to do something so despicable.

64
00:05:53,839 --> 00:05:54,519
Lu Daozai,

65
00:05:55,560 --> 00:05:57,120
have you and your son no shame at all?

66
00:05:58,120 --> 00:06:01,360
Would your own son work for your worst enemy?

67
00:06:01,360 --> 00:06:02,800
You have the nerve to put on this act,

68
00:06:02,800 --> 00:06:03,839
but I'm too embarrassed to watch.

69
00:06:04,199 --> 00:06:05,319
If you don't believe me, ask him yourself.

70
00:06:06,160 --> 00:06:07,240
You just don't understand

71
00:06:07,240 --> 00:06:08,680
the pain of useless people like us.

72
00:06:09,439 --> 00:06:10,759
My sister is better than me.

73
00:06:10,759 --> 00:06:12,040
My father craves power.

74
00:06:12,040 --> 00:06:14,240
I study like a dog every day,

75
00:06:14,240 --> 00:06:16,120
but I just can't learn it.

76
00:06:16,399 --> 00:06:18,199
There's no future for me in this family.

77
00:06:18,959 --> 00:06:21,439
That actually doesn't sound like nonsense.

78
00:06:21,439 --> 00:06:22,399
If that's the case,

79
00:06:22,399 --> 00:06:23,680
he really might have defected to Green Wood Hall.

80
00:06:27,879 --> 00:06:29,319
What's wrong?

81
00:06:29,319 --> 00:06:30,079
Angry now?

82
00:06:30,920 --> 00:06:32,560
With acting skills like yours,

83
00:06:32,560 --> 00:06:34,040
it'd be a waste not to be an actor.

84
00:06:36,480 --> 00:06:39,079
He's a useless nobody.

85
00:06:39,079 --> 00:06:41,639
You think Green Wood Hall would value him?

86
00:06:42,439 --> 00:06:43,519
Are you all blind?

87
00:06:45,279 --> 00:06:46,800
Green Wood Hall is different, of course.

88
00:06:48,360 --> 00:06:49,920
Father and daughter at odds,

89
00:06:49,920 --> 00:06:51,439
no successor in sight.

90
00:06:51,439 --> 00:06:52,639
As long as I'm loyal,

91
00:06:52,639 --> 00:06:54,360
I'll naturally get a chance to rise.

92
00:06:58,040 --> 00:06:59,360
Uncle Ye!

93
00:06:59,360 --> 00:07:00,519
You can't just toss me aside after using me!

94
00:07:00,519 --> 00:07:01,720
Uncle Ye!

95
00:07:01,720 --> 00:07:03,959
You're talking nonsense!

96
00:07:11,480 --> 00:07:12,480
Fine then!

97
00:07:14,079 --> 00:07:15,279
You old scoundrel!

98
00:07:15,959 --> 00:07:16,480
You...

99
00:07:17,079 --> 00:07:18,399
Since you turned on me first,

100
00:07:19,480 --> 00:07:20,680
don't blame me for being ruthless.

101
00:07:23,759 --> 00:07:25,680
I, Lu Mingcheng, hereby formally accuse

102
00:07:25,959 --> 00:07:28,759
Medicine Master Ye Zhentian,

103
00:07:28,759 --> 00:07:31,079
of sabotaging the Medicine King Ceremony!

104
00:07:31,480 --> 00:07:32,040
You...

105
00:07:32,959 --> 00:07:33,519
You...

106
00:07:34,199 --> 00:07:35,439
Father!

107
00:07:36,600 --> 00:07:37,040
Father!

108
00:07:41,040 --> 00:07:42,399
Uncle Ye!

109
00:07:42,399 --> 00:07:43,439
Uncle Ye!

110
00:07:43,439 --> 00:07:44,000
Father!

111
00:07:44,000 --> 00:07:45,720
Uncle Ye!

112
00:07:45,720 --> 00:07:47,920
Uncle Ye, you can't just leave after using me!

113
00:07:47,920 --> 00:07:49,519
If you're gone, how will I clear my name?

114
00:07:49,519 --> 00:07:55,040
Uncle Ye!

115
00:07:55,040 --> 00:07:56,319
Father!

116
00:07:56,879 --> 00:07:58,240
Uncle Ye!

117
00:08:01,439 --> 00:08:02,279
Yunfan!

118
00:08:06,879 --> 00:08:07,800
Yunfan!

119
00:08:08,720 --> 00:08:09,639
Yunfan!

120
00:08:11,560 --> 00:08:12,600
Yunfan!

121
00:08:13,040 --> 00:08:13,959
Father, hold on!

122
00:08:14,360 --> 00:08:15,160
Father!

123
00:08:18,720 --> 00:08:19,439
Yunfan!

124
00:08:19,439 --> 00:08:20,399
Father, are you okay?

125
00:08:20,399 --> 00:08:21,240
Don't scare me!

126
00:08:24,839 --> 00:08:26,360
Haven't you caused enough trouble?

127
00:08:27,240 --> 00:08:28,120
Get out!

128
00:08:28,120 --> 00:08:29,079
That's enough.

129
00:08:30,600 --> 00:08:31,519
Stop

130
00:08:31,519 --> 00:08:33,200
disturbing Medicine Master Ye's recovery.

131
00:08:33,200 --> 00:08:34,080
Let's go.

132
00:08:36,600 --> 00:08:37,720
Uncle Ye!

133
00:08:38,200 --> 00:08:38,720
Father!

134
00:08:59,840 --> 00:09:00,480
Yunfan

135
00:09:08,879 --> 00:09:09,559
Dad!

136
00:09:14,159 --> 00:09:14,840
Dad!

137
00:09:27,120 --> 00:09:27,799
Dad!

138
00:09:42,919 --> 00:09:43,360
Dad!

139
00:10:26,480 --> 00:10:28,919
The eldest daughter pays her respects.

140
00:10:38,000 --> 00:10:39,360
For this final farewell,

141
00:10:40,120 --> 00:10:42,799
how could we old friends not see him off

142
00:10:42,799 --> 00:10:44,480
before the funeral procession?

143
00:11:09,000 --> 00:11:10,519
A funeral is underway.

144
00:11:10,519 --> 00:11:12,080
Let's avoid any disputes.

145
00:11:17,399 --> 00:11:19,519
With Brother Ye gone,

146
00:11:19,519 --> 00:11:21,039
the Mystic Medicine Association

147
00:11:21,039 --> 00:11:23,720
will lose its true scholar of the Ancient Method.

148
00:11:24,519 --> 00:11:26,240
What a pity.

149
00:11:26,240 --> 00:11:27,840
Such a shame.

150
00:11:40,279 --> 00:11:42,840
With Medicine Master Ye gone,

151
00:11:43,799 --> 00:11:46,639
Green Wood Hall needs its order restored.

152
00:11:50,200 --> 00:11:51,519
If Pharmacy Master Li is here to pay respects,

153
00:11:52,240 --> 00:11:52,799
you're welcome.

154
00:11:53,919 --> 00:11:56,519
But if you have other intentions, please leave.

155
00:11:57,919 --> 00:11:59,600
Medicine Master Ye left no final orders.

156
00:12:00,200 --> 00:12:01,879
It's not your place to take charge.

157
00:12:02,759 --> 00:12:04,080
See?

158
00:12:04,080 --> 00:12:05,200
What did I tell you?

159
00:12:06,080 --> 00:12:08,039
Now any random nobody dares to call the shots.

160
00:12:08,840 --> 00:12:09,559
That's why

161
00:12:09,559 --> 00:12:10,600
we must

162
00:12:10,600 --> 00:12:12,080
find someone to take over right away.

163
00:12:12,879 --> 00:12:14,000
And properly restore discipline.

164
00:12:18,519 --> 00:12:20,360
My father did want to leave his final orders.

165
00:12:22,039 --> 00:12:23,799
But did you ever give him the chance?

166
00:12:28,120 --> 00:12:30,080
From this day forward,

167
00:12:30,080 --> 00:12:32,240
all affairs of Green Wood Hall

168
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,799
will be managed by me, Ye Qingxue.

169
00:12:34,679 --> 00:12:37,960
I will shoulder this responsibility myself.

170
00:12:42,600 --> 00:12:43,799
Qingxue,

171
00:12:44,120 --> 00:12:47,279
the poisoning at the Ceremony is unsolved.

172
00:12:47,279 --> 00:12:49,639
Green Wood Hall is in a state of unrest.

173
00:12:49,639 --> 00:12:52,480
And you've just suffered a heavy loss.

174
00:12:52,480 --> 00:12:55,559
I fear you can't handle these duties alone.

175
00:12:57,759 --> 00:12:58,399
Xiang, my son,

176
00:12:59,120 --> 00:13:01,360
go and help share Qingxue's burden.

177
00:13:01,360 --> 00:13:03,080
Assist with Green Wood Hall's medical affairs.

178
00:13:03,080 --> 00:13:04,679
No problem, Father.

179
00:13:04,679 --> 00:13:06,240
I'll devote my full effort to it.

180
00:13:07,759 --> 00:13:09,519
Quite the scheme you've cooked up.

181
00:13:10,639 --> 00:13:12,639
You're a Medicine Holder of Red Fire Hall.

182
00:13:12,639 --> 00:13:14,440
Meddling in Green Wood Hall's affairs now?

183
00:13:15,200 --> 00:13:16,000
Who do you think you are?

184
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,720
You have no right to speak here.

185
00:13:21,519 --> 00:13:22,720
I'm the son-in-law of the Ye family.

186
00:13:24,720 --> 00:13:25,919
Yang Yunfan.

187
00:13:43,240 --> 00:13:44,279
What?

188
00:13:44,279 --> 00:13:46,159
Addicted to acting now?

189
00:13:46,159 --> 00:13:48,440
Do you really think you're their son-in-law?

190
00:13:51,600 --> 00:13:52,399
What's going on?

191
00:13:53,200 --> 00:13:54,759
Isn't he Yang Yunfan?

192
00:13:54,759 --> 00:13:56,200
You actually believe that?

193
00:13:56,519 --> 00:13:59,120
He's likely an actor Ye Qingxue hired.

194
00:13:59,120 --> 00:14:00,600
This isn't Yang Yunfan.

195
00:14:00,600 --> 00:14:01,320
The whole thing about those two

196
00:14:01,320 --> 00:14:02,279
has the Association in an uproar.

197
00:14:02,279 --> 00:14:03,799
Yeah, I heard about it ages ago.

198
00:14:05,519 --> 00:14:07,879
I recall when the Yang family was wiped out,

199
00:14:07,879 --> 00:14:09,639
no surviving heir was ever confirmed.

200
00:14:10,679 --> 00:14:12,600
So this Yang Yunfan of yours,

201
00:14:12,600 --> 00:14:15,240
if he can't even produce a birth certificate,

202
00:14:15,240 --> 00:14:17,720
that's a clear breach of protocol, isn't it?

203
00:14:19,960 --> 00:14:22,279
The Yang family matter may be long past,

204
00:14:22,279 --> 00:14:23,960
but it concerns lineage and bloodline.

205
00:14:24,919 --> 00:14:25,960
There's no room for error.

206
00:14:28,519 --> 00:14:29,440
Green Wood Hall

207
00:14:30,120 --> 00:14:31,399
cannot entrust its medical affairs

208
00:14:31,399 --> 00:14:33,679
to someone of unknown identity.

209
00:14:34,559 --> 00:14:35,919
My father's funeral is being held today.

210
00:14:40,919 --> 00:14:42,279
We mustn't miss the auspicious hour.

211
00:14:43,200 --> 00:14:44,360
Esteemed elders, please take your leave.

212
00:14:44,919 --> 00:14:45,679
Show them out.

213
00:14:55,320 --> 00:14:57,360
Qingxue,

214
00:14:57,360 --> 00:14:59,080
the truth won't change.

215
00:14:59,919 --> 00:15:02,279
What needs to be clarified

216
00:15:02,279 --> 00:15:03,840
will come to light sooner or later.

217
00:15:27,519 --> 00:15:28,320
Qingxue.

218
00:15:42,600 --> 00:15:43,519
I'm here to pick up the medicine.

219
00:15:49,039 --> 00:15:49,960
Son-in-law.

220
00:16:06,879 --> 00:16:08,039
This is the last vial of medicine.

221
00:16:10,279 --> 00:16:10,960
Useless fool!

222
00:16:14,399 --> 00:16:16,720
You failed to get the Primordial Chaos Violet Qi Art!

223
00:16:16,720 --> 00:16:18,759
And you lost the Sea-Pacifying Mind Art!

224
00:16:19,799 --> 00:16:21,159
Or else my Xiang wouldn't suffer like this.

225
00:16:22,399 --> 00:16:23,879
Rest assured, my dear in-law.

226
00:16:23,879 --> 00:16:25,120
At tomorrow's Path of Healing,

227
00:16:25,120 --> 00:16:27,559
we will surely safeguard Xiang.

228
00:16:27,559 --> 00:16:28,559
We'll make sure he passes the test

229
00:16:28,559 --> 00:16:30,039
to get the Primordial Chaos Violet Qi Art.

230
00:16:33,000 --> 00:16:33,600
By the way,

231
00:16:34,440 --> 00:16:37,679
Will that brat Yang Yunfan crash it tomorrow?

232
00:16:39,720 --> 00:16:41,960
He's a fraud with no real identity.

233
00:16:43,320 --> 00:16:46,960
Even if he shows up, shut him out.

234
00:16:46,960 --> 00:16:48,320
Yes.

235
00:16:48,320 --> 00:16:49,600
My son-in-law is right.

236
00:16:49,600 --> 00:16:51,000
That brat can't get in at all.

237
00:16:51,960 --> 00:16:52,919
It's in the bag now.

238
00:16:52,919 --> 00:16:53,559
It's in the bag now.

239
00:16:54,399 --> 00:16:54,919
Indeed.

240
00:17:05,359 --> 00:17:07,119
Due to the Medicine King Ceremony incident

241
00:17:07,119 --> 00:17:08,920
and the crisis at Green Wood Hall,

242
00:17:08,920 --> 00:17:10,359
for the sake of the bigger picture,

243
00:17:10,359 --> 00:17:13,519
the Mystic Medicine Association elders decided

244
00:17:13,519 --> 00:17:14,920
to merge the Medicine Holder assessment

245
00:17:14,920 --> 00:17:17,119
with Path of Healing round one.

246
00:17:18,960 --> 00:17:20,519
No wonder we got the notice.

247
00:17:20,920 --> 00:17:22,359
What a stroke of luck.

248
00:17:22,359 --> 00:17:25,200
I thought making Medicine Holder was hopeless.

249
00:17:25,200 --> 00:17:26,440
Didn't expect to get a make-up exam.

250
00:17:27,480 --> 00:17:28,240
That's pretty good.

251
00:17:28,240 --> 00:17:29,119
We caught it just in time.

252
00:17:30,480 --> 00:17:31,640
Look at that Ye Qingxue.

253
00:17:31,640 --> 00:17:33,279
Why is that fake Yang family heir here too?

254
00:17:43,319 --> 00:17:44,160
Feng Shun.

255
00:17:44,160 --> 00:17:44,960
Why are they here?

256
00:17:51,960 --> 00:17:53,720
If I remember correctly,

257
00:17:54,720 --> 00:17:57,880
anyone unverified by the Mystic Medicine Association

258
00:17:58,400 --> 00:17:59,759
cannot register for the Path of Healing.

259
00:18:01,519 --> 00:18:02,319
Sorry to disappoint.

260
00:18:03,279 --> 00:18:05,559
This time, I actually brought proof.
